2002-1977 (La. 10/25/02)

Paula DUNN v. RIVERVIEW MEDICAL CENTER. No. 2002-C-1977. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re Riverview Medical Center; — Defendant; Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review Office Of Workers’ Compensation District 5, No. 00-01238; to the Court of Appeal, First Circuit, No. 2001 CA 1521.

Denied.

VICTORY, J., would grant the writ. TRAYLOR, J., would grant the writ.
